{"tid":694628,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾與奧巴馬共餐】美國名廚波登自殺身亡 終年61歲","createTime":"2018-06-08T13:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T13:30:14.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5fbb2864d347ee81b5e7dac9099b492fb7aeb7","tid":694628,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:20:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180608/58294554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58294554&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=40d7a99e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F58294554&h=aefaf2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180608/58294554</a><br />\n<br />\n蒜頭可以用腳踩~細過學廚比 CF 打到痴肺....<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）報道，美國名廚波登（Anthony Bourdain）自殺身亡，終年61歲。<br />\n<br />\n波登出事時正身在法國史特拉斯堡，正為CNN新一季節目進行拍攝。他的好友、法國廚師Eric Ripert周五早上到波登的酒店房間，發現他在房內上吊自殺。<br />\nCNN發表聲明，讚揚波登熱愛冒險，喜愛美酒佳餚及認識新朋友，指他的才華令人驚訝，對他的離世感到十分可惜。<br />\n波登除了是名廚外，亦是CNN的節目主持。2016年5月他與正在越南訪問的美國總統奧巴馬，一起到河內一間平民小店吃烤肉米線和飲啤酒，討論奧巴馬亞洲之行，波登之後將與奧巴馬共餐的圖片放上網，讚奧巴馬很會用筷子。<br />\n波登與前妻育有一名女兒，他去年起與意大利女星艾莎阿基多（Asia Argento）發展戀情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4488f287673e50c8e21350e1561149059b27cd77","tid":694628,"uid":170668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}